featured_reviews.review_id:
Compact. Struggle. Reference.

The sermons given here are primarily based on the authentic references. In a small place, they have struggled to build the mosque.

Poor administration. Unprofessional management. Egocentric.

Because of lack of in-depth knowledge and wisdom, people here lack proper leadership.

Overall, it is one of the best places in the entire city of Ujjain to come close to the genuine teachings of Islaam.

And all praises to God.
